abstract: >
  FedAgent-Chain is a secure federated and agentic AI framework for
  multilingual, disability-inclusive employment intelligence in AI-driven
  smart cities. It unifies federated learning, permissioned blockchain
  auditability, agentic AI coordination, multilingual NLP, and
  human-in-the-loop governance.
